'''Connie Temweka Gabisile Chiume''' (yavutse ku ya 5 Kamena 1952) ni umukinnyi wa filime wo muri Afurika yepfo  <ref name="briefly">https://briefly.co.za/37398-connie-chiume-biography-age-date-birth-nationality-husband-parents-nominations-awards-tv-shows-movies-instagram-contact-details.html</ref> Azwiho gukina film muri ''Black Panther'', ''Black Is King'' na ''Blessers'' . Kuri tereviziyo, yagaragaye muri ''Zone 14'', ''Umujyi wa Rhythm'', na ''Gomora'' .

== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Chiume yavukiye i Welkom muri Afurika y'Epfo. <ref name="studentroom">https://www.studentroom.co.za/wiki/connie-chiume/</ref> Se wa Wright Tadeyo Chiume (m. 1983) yakomokaga muri Usisya, Nkhata Bay, [[Malawi]] na nyina MaNdlovu (m. 2020) <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/former-rhythm-city-actress-connie-chiume-mourns-her-mother-20200318</ref> bakomoka i KwaZulu-Natal, muri Afurika y'Epfo. Mubyara weEfurayimu Mganda Chiume wo muri [[Malawi]] .

Chiume yamaze ubwana bwe muri Welkom. Yarangije matriche mu burasirazuba bwa Cape  impamyabumenyi yo kwigisha mu 1976. Amaze imyaka mike yigisha, yaretse ingendo yimukira mu Bugereki. <ref name="briefly" />

== Umwuga ==
Chiume yatangiye umwuga we wo gukina afite uruhare muri ''Porgy na Bess'', ''Ipi Ntombi'', na ''Shop Ntoya ya Horrors'' .  Amaze gusubira muri Afurika y'Epfo, yatowe nka Thembi mu rukurikirane rwo mu 1989 ''Inkom 'Edla Yodwa'' hanyuma filime yo mu 1990 yitwa ''Warriors from Hell'' . Mu 2000, yatsindiye igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza muri serivise yikinamico muri Afurika yepfo ya Filime na seri za  Televiziyo . 

Muri 2006, yakinnye mubikorwa bya stage ''Wakubise Umugore'' ''nawe Ukubita Urutare'' .  Kuva 2007 kugeza 2015, Chiume yamenyekanye cyane kubera uruhare rwe nka Stella Moloi muri SABC1 ikinamico ya ''Zone 14'', yamuhesheje indi SAFTA. <ref name="studentroom" /> Yabonye kandi igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza muri Drama mugihe cya 3 SAFTA. Muri 2015, yagaragaye muri opera yisabune ''Rhythm City'' nka Mamokete Khuse. 

Muri 2018, Chiume yakinnye Mining Tribe Umusaza muri Marvel Cinematic Universe film ''Black Panther'' . <ref>https://www.news24.com/channel/movies/news/south-africas-film-industry-needs-to-reach-for-the-stars-20180106</ref> <ref>https://www.news24.com/channel/movies/news/local-actress-connie-chiume-ready-to-meet-co-stars-at-black-panther-premiere-20180103</ref>

Muri 2020, Chiume yinjiye mu mwanya wa Mam'Sonto Molefe mu rukurikirane ''rw'ikinamico Gomora'' maze agaragara muri filime ''Black Is King'' . <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/news/connie-chiume-on-black-is-king-and-her-role-as-a-fussy-mother-in-netflixs-seriously-single-20200807</ref> Mu Kwakira 2020, yabonye igihembo cya Feather Award. <ref>https://www.news24.com/citypress/trending/actress-connie-chiume-honoured-with-first-feather-award-nomination-20201015</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Chiume yashakanye kuva 1985 kugeza 2004. Ni nyina w'abana bane, afite abahungu babiri n'abakobwa babiri. 

